data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch home on a spacious lot with a rocking chair front porch! You'll immediately be greeted with vaulted ceilings in the family room with hardwood floors featuring the large fireplace as the focal point of the room. The breakfast area is off of the kitchen that has new counter tops, stainless steel appliances and a sink at the  window overlooking the spacious backyard. The owners suite features a walk-in closet and en suite bathroom. The interior of this home is complete with two additional bedrooms and full bathrooms. In the backyard is the newly painted deck perfect for entertaining family and friends!
